---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Kekasatori — Terms of Sale & Refund Policy"
  description="How buying Kekasatori works: pricing, license delivery, and the 14-day refund policy."
>
  <div class="page-container py-16 md:py-24">
    <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <a href="/projects/kekasatori" class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] no-underline">← Kekasatori</a>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl">Terms of Sale &amp; Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Effective 12 July 2026 · Contact: harikanth.ai@outlook.com</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">Who you are buying from</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Kekasatori is sold by Harikanth Lingutla, an independent developer ("the developer", "we").
            Questions about any purchase: harikanth.ai@outlook.com.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">What you are buying</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            You are buying a personal license key for the Kekasatori macOS app, as described in the
            <a href="/kekasatori/terms">Terms of Use</a>. The license is perpetual for the versions it covers
            and includes all updates to the current major version. The price and any applicable taxes are
            shown at checkout before you pay.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">Payment &amp; delivery</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Payments are processed securely by <a href="https://stripe.com">Stripe</a>; we never see or store
            your card details. Your license key is delivered immediately after checkout — shown on the
            confirmation page and emailed to the address you used at purchase. If it doesn't arrive within a
            few minutes, check your spam folder, then email us and we'll re-send it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">Try before you buy</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Kekasatori offers a free trial so you can make sure it works for you — your Mac, your workflow,
            your providers — before paying anything.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">14-day refund policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If Kekasatori isn't for you, email harikanth.ai@outlook.com within <strong
            class="text-[var(--color-ink)]">14 days of purchase</strong> from the email address you bought
            with (or include your receipt), and we'll refund you in full — no questions asked. Refunds go
            back to the original payment method; your license key is deactivated once the refund is issued.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If you're in the EU or UK: you have a statutory 14-day right of withdrawal for digital content.
            By retrieving your license key immediately at checkout you consent to immediate supply — but our
            voluntary 14-day refund policy above applies regardless, so you lose nothing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-[var(--color-ink)]">Problems &amp; disputes</h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            If anything goes wrong — a failed download, a key that won't activate, a double charge — please
            contact us first; almost everything can be fixed within a day, and refunds are honored per the
            policy above without needing a card dispute.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
